FROM (

) AS [t]

) AS [t]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [restaurantBranches] AS [r0] ON [t].[Id] = [r0].[RestaurantId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]

SELECT [r].[Id] AS [BranchId], [d].[Capacity], [d].[TableName], [t].[MealType], [t].[ReservationDay], [t].[TableStatus], [t].[Id] AS [TimeSlotId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) LOWER([a].[Email])
    FROM [reservations] AS [r0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [r0].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
    WHERE [r0].[TimeSlotId] = [t].[Id]) AS [UserEmailId]
FROM [restaurantBranches] AS [r]
INNER JOIN [dinnerTables] AS [d] ON [r].[Id] = [d].[RestaurantBranchId]
INNER JOIN [timeSlots] AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DinnerTableId]
WHERE ([d].[RestaurantBranchId] = @__branchId_0) AND ([t].[ReservationDay] >= CONVERT(date, GETDATE()))
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[MealType]

2024-10-19 14:51:01.230 +05:00 [INF] Entity Framework Core 6.0.18 initialized 'AppDbContext' using provider 'Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer:6.0.18' with options: None
2024-10-19 14:51:01.242 +05:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (8ms) [Parameters=[@__branchId_0='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [r].[Id] AS [BranchId], [d].[Capacity], [d].[TableName], [t].[MealType], [t].[ReservationDay], [t].[TableStatus], [t].[Id] AS [TimeSlotId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) LOWER([a].[Email])
    FROM [reservations] AS [r0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [r0].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
    WHERE [r0].[TimeSlotId] = [t].[Id]) AS [UserEmailId]
FROM [restaurantBranches] AS [r]
INNER JOIN [dinnerTables] AS [d] ON [r].[Id] = [d].[RestaurantBranchId]
INNER JOIN [timeSlots] AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DinnerTableId]
WHERE ([d].[RestaurantBranchId] = @__branchId_0) AND ([t].[ReservationDay] >= CONVERT(date, GETDATE()))
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[MealType]

SELECT [r].[Id] AS [BranchId], [d].[Capacity], [d].[TableName], [t].[MealType], [t].[ReservationDay], [t].[TableStatus], [t].[Id] AS [TimeSlotId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) LOWER([a].[Email])
    FROM [reservations] AS [r0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [r0].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
    WHERE [r0].[TimeSlotId] = [t].[Id]) AS [UserEmailId]
FROM [restaurantBranches] AS [r]
INNER JOIN [dinnerTables] AS [d] ON [r].[Id] = [d].[RestaurantBranchId]
INNER JOIN [timeSlots] AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DinnerTableId]
WHERE ([d].[RestaurantBranchId] = @__branchId_0) AND ([t].[ReservationDay] >= CONVERT(date, GETDATE()))
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[MealType]

    SELECT TOP(1) LOWER([a].[Email])
    FROM [reservations] AS [r0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [r0].[UserId] = [a].[Id]

FROM [restaurantBranches] AS [r]
INNER JOIN [dinnerTables] AS [d] ON [r].[Id] = [d].[RestaurantBranchId]
INNER JOIN [timeSlots] AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DinnerTableId]

SELECT [r].[Id] AS [BranchId], [d].[Capacity], [d].[TableName], [t].[MealType], [t].[ReservationDay], [t].[TableStatus], [t].[Id] AS [TimeSlotId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) LOWER([a].[Email])
    FROM [reservations] AS [r0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [r0].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
    WHERE [r0].[TimeSlotId] = [t].[Id]) AS [UserEmailId]
FROM [restaurantBranches] AS [r]
INNER JOIN [dinnerTables] AS [d] ON [r].[Id] = [d].[RestaurantBranchId]
INNER JOIN [timeSlots] AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DinnerTableId]
WHERE ([d].[RestaurantBranchId] = @__branchId_0) AND ([t].[ReservationDay] >= CONVERT(date, GETDATE()))
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[MealType]

SELECT [r].[Id] AS [BranchId], [d].[Capacity], [d].[TableName], [t].[MealType], [t].[ReservationDay], [t].[TableStatus], [t].[Id] AS [TimeSlotId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) LOWER([a].[Email])
    FROM [reservations] AS [r0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [r0].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
    WHERE [r0].[TimeSlotId] = [t].[Id]) AS [UserEmailId]

INNER JOIN [dinnerTables] AS [d] ON [r].[Id] = [d].[RestaurantBranchId]
INNER JOIN [timeSlots] AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DinnerTableId]
WHERE ([d].[RestaurantBranchId] = @__branchId_0) AND ([t].[ReservationDay] >= CONVERT(date, GETDATE()))
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[MealType]

    SELECT TOP(1) LOWER([a].[Email])

SELECT [r].[Id] AS [BranchId], [d].[Capacity], [d].[TableName], [t].[MealType], [t].[ReservationDay], [t].[TableStatus], [t].[Id] AS [TimeSlotId], (
    SELECT TOP(1) LOWER([a].[Email])
    FROM [reservations] AS [r0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [r0].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
    WHERE [r0].[TimeSlotId] = [t].[Id]) AS [UserEmailId]
FROM [restaurantBranches] AS [r]
INNER JOIN [dinnerTables] AS [d] ON [r].[Id] = [d].[RestaurantBranchId]
INNER JOIN [timeSlots] AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DinnerTableId]
WHERE ([d].[RestaurantBranchId] = @__branchId_0) AND ([t].[ReservationDay] >= CONVERT(date, GETDATE()))
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[MealType]
